OL,6,FAlicia Hardie, whose daughter Cora
OL,7,FDonohue was born three weeks early on
OL,8,FChristmas Eve, is one mother who has
OL,9,Fwelcomed the service, along with her
OL,10,Fpartner Mark Donohue.
OL,12,FMiss Hardie, from Kilbarchan,
OL,13,FRenfrewshire, said: "I gave birth at
OL,14,Fthe Royal Alexandra Hospital and had
OL,15,Flost a lot of blood, so I needed to
OL,16,Fstay in for a few days afterwards.
