OL,6,F"We were all packed up and ready to go
OL,7,Fhome when Cora's blood test showed she
OL,8,Fneeded light therapy for jaundice. At
OL,9,Fthat point, we didn't know the
OL,10,FHospital at Home service existed, so
OL,11,Fwe stayed in for another few days.
OL,13,F"We finally got home on December 30,
OL,14,Fbut at Cora's next blood test her
OL,15,Fjaundice levels were still high, and
OL,16,Fshe needed the lights again, so back
OL,17,Fto hospital we went. It was during
OL,18,Fthat stay that the team told us about
OL,19,Fthe Hospital at Home equipment.
