OL,3,CNewborns with jaundice treated at home
OL,4,Cin sleeping bag-style garment
OL,6,F"Within two hours of learning about
OL,7,Fit, senior nurse Kerry was giving us
OL,8,Feverything we needed.
OL,10,F"After an early birth and the back and
OL,11,Fforth for blood tests, it was exactly
OL,12,Fwhat we needed. We could finally relax
OL,13,Fat home and start our new life
OL,14,Ftogether.
OL,16,F"Kerry was so supportive, and the
OL,17,Fequipment was incredibly easy to use.
OL,18,FAfter just two days using the suit at
OL,19,Fhome, Cora passed her blood test and
OL,20,Fshe's doing brilliantly now."
