OL,6,FThe dedicated team delivering the
OL,7,Finitiative comprises four neonatal
OL,8,FHospital at Home senior nurses, four
OL,9,Fconsultants and a service improvement
OL,10,Fmanager.
OL,12,FThey currently have six units and
OL,13,Ftreatment length varies from two to
OL,14,Feight days, but is dependent on
OL,15,Findividual results from each baby.
