OL,6,FNHS Greater Glasgow and Clyde (NHSGGC)
OL,7,Fneonatal Hospital at Home senior nurse
OL,8,FKayleigh Cunningham said: "Hospital at
OL,9,FHome helps us treat babies who may
OL,10,Fdevelop jaundice symptoms around 72
OL,11,Fhours after birth, as this can happen
OL,12,Foften.
OL,14,F"If a mum and baby have already gone
OL,15,Fhome, they would traditionally need to
OL,16,Freturn for a hospital stay.
OL,18,F"This can be upsetting when families
OL,19,Fhave just begun settling into life at
OL,20,Fhome."
