OL,6,FThe programme was designed and
OL,7,Fdeveloped by the hospital's neonatal
OL,8,Fteam following a successful three-
OL,9,Fmonth pilot in 2024.
OL,11,FNHSGGC said its community midwives
OL,12,Fwill continue to screen for jaundice
OL,13,Fduring routine home visits, ensuring
OL,14,Feligible babies can be referred
OL,15,Fswiftly to the new service.
